{
  "stem": "8834.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a terrible tragedy to our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we heard it, it was devastating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from then on, we-- we saw--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not witness it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw it before I went down to see him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was terrible, a terrible shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know what happens further after.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this-- this incident I remember vividly, that they found that radio in the-- in his place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, ?] terrible, terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- they went-- he had six sons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the son went-- the sons went on hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three sons went on hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- they found the hiding place later, and they took them out and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not three.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They shot two, and one was alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't see the-- the third one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these people-- and one-- one is survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was hiding in a big city as a barber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he looked like a gentile, so he survived the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their names?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Itzhak Mayer, Moshe [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cousins, Herling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one survive, and one was-- was hidden as a barber in a big city survived, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were-- till this day they never re-married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were depressed and couldn't get on with life-- what they saw, what they witnessed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They still live in New York State, and I write to them sometimes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they write to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they never married because of what they saw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were in a terrible, terrible state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, ?] took everybody to work for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they cut the beards from all the men, the religious men, everyone, and their beard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they cut it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't cut it straight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They cut it with a piece of flesh, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
